<a name="ring_of_the_ancients"></a>
<font color="#FFFFFF" face="Arial">
<strong>Ring of the Ancients - AC 6</strong>
<font size=-1></font><BR>
Slot: <a href="/armour/wrists.shtml">Wrists</a><BR>
Weight: 2.0 - All Races<BR>
Classes: <a href="/bard/armour/wrists.shtml">BRD</a>, <a href="/cleric/armour/wrists.shtml">CLR</a>, <a href="/druid/armour/wrists.shtml">DRU</a>, <a href="/enchanter/armour/wrists.shtml">ENC</a>, <a href="/magician/armour/wrists.shtml">MAG</a>, <a href="/monk/armour/wrists.shtml">MNK</a>, <a href="/necromancer/armour/wrists.shtml">NEC</a>, <a href="/paladin/armour/wrists.shtml">PAL</a>, <a href="/ranger/armour/wrists.shtml">RNG</a>, <a href="/rogue/armour/wrists.shtml">ROG</a>, <a href="/shadow_knight/armour/wrists.shtml">SHD</a>, <a href="/shaman/armour/wrists.shtml">SHM</a>, <a href="/warrior/armour/wrists.shtml">WAR</a>, <a href="/wizard/armour/wrists.shtml">WIZ</a><BR>
<font color=red>
(Magic) (No Drop) (Lore) <BR>
(INT +5) </font>
<BR>
Dropped by the Ancient Cyclops in various zones.<BR>

